ADDITIONAL NOTES

The code in this directory is provided as educational material to help make
LaTeX documents more accessible. Feel free to:

- Use these tools in your own projects
- Modify them to fit your needs
- Share them with others
- Include them in larger projects
- Use them commercially

We only ask that you:
- Give appropriate credit
- Share improvements back to the community when possible
- Help make the web more accessible!

For questions or to share improvements, please visit:
https://github.com/aholdengouveia or https://aholdengouveia.name
